node.text: Today, I want to highlight the importance of voter protection at the polls. @wetheactionorg is deploying lawyers to polling places across the country to ensure our votes are protected. I have many wonderful lawyers in my life who have already volunteered their time to protect our votes. If you’re a lawyer or know a lawyer, please sign up for or share We The Action!

node.text: The day we released "Cheek To Cheek" in 2014, @itstonybennett called me and asked me if I wanted to record another album with him, this time celebrating the songs of Cole Porter. I'm always honored to sing with my friend Tony, so of course I accepted the invitation. Today, I am so excited to announce that our new album "Love For Sale" will be released October 1. You can pre-order the album and listen to our first single "I Get A Kick Out Of You" everywhere now!
